  "narration": "Welcome back, Eirik. The early morning light filters softly through the windows of the Black Lantern Hearth, casting a warm glow across the room. Your companions--Kira, Elen, and Thane--are already gathered near the hearth, their expressions a mix of calm determination and quiet vigilance. The air carries the familiar scents of peat smoke and the salty sea breeze drifting in from the coast. Outside, the village slowly stirs awake as the promise of a new day unfolds.\n\nWhat would you like to do as you prepare for the challenges ahead? Discuss your plans with the party, seek out information from Elder Dorun or Captain Merek, or venture forth toward the abbey ruins and lighthouse?",
