{
  "narration": "You gather around the familiar hearth of the Black Lantern Hearth, the comforting warmth of the peat fire casting a golden glow on the rough-hewn wooden tables. The air is thick with the scent of ale and smoked stew, and the quiet murmurs of villagers blend with the crackle of burning logs. Scout Kira raises her mug with a playful smirk. \"To us,\" she toasts, \"and to facing whatever the cursed cliffs throw at us next.\"\n\nElen gives a nod of agreement, her keen eyes reflecting the firelight, while Thane quietly lifts his mug in a steady salute. Eirik, your steady presence among them, feels the bond of camaraderie strengthen with each shared sip and smile. Around you, the Hearth's patrons glance your way with hopeful eyes, their faith in your resolve palpable.\n\nThe moment offers a brief respite, a chance to relax and share stories, before the storm of the abbey and lighthouse awaits. As the ale warms your spirits, what would you like to discuss or plan for next?",
