  "narration": "Welcome back, Eirik. The Black Lantern Hearth remains a warm refuge amid the salt-kissed air and flickering hearthlight. Your companions--Kira, Elen, and Thane--are gathered nearby, their expressions a blend of quiet resolve and anticipation. The village outside hums softly with the rhythm of daily life, but within these walls, the weight of your shared journey feels a little lighter.\n\nWhat would you like to do next? Would you like to discuss your next course of action, seek out Elder Dorun or Captain Merek for news, or prepare to venture once more toward the abbey ruins and lighthouse?",
