{
  "narration": "You head to the hearthside table within the Black Lantern Hearth, the warm glow of the peat fire casting flickering shadows across the worn wooden beams. Around you, the tavern hums with quiet chatter and the comforting aroma of simmering stew and fresh bread fills the air. Scout Kira settles beside you with a relieved sigh, while Elen surveys the room with a watchful eye. Thane nods in approval at the familiar comfort.\n\nAn unnamed server promptly arrives with steaming bowls of rich, hearty stew filled with root vegetables and salted fish, accompanied by thick slices of crusty bread. The warmth of the meal seeps into your hands as you take your first bite, the flavors hearty and grounding after your recent trials.\n\nAs you eat, the familiar atmosphere of the Hearth reminds you of the fragile peace in Marrow's Rest and the tenuous hope that your efforts inspire among the villagers. The soft murmur of conversation around you ebbs and flows, punctuated by the occasional clatter of mugs and laughter.\n\nWhat would you like to do after your meal? Would you like to speak with Elder Dorun, gather information from Scout Kira, or prepare for your next journey?",
