{
  "narration": "You and Kira, wrapped in the soft hush of the pre-dawn hours, settle together and allow exhaustion to claim you. As the gentle darkness of the Black Lantern Hearth gives way to the golden warmth of late morning, your sleep is uninterrupted by worry or fear. Sunlight streams through the tavern's small window, casting shifting patterns on the wall as you awaken refreshed. Kira stirs beside you, her expression peaceful, and the quiet sounds of Marrow's Rest signal a new day.\n\nDownstairs, you can hear the faint clatter of mugs and the low hum of villagers beginning their routines. Thane and Elen are already up, voices low as they prepare for whatever the new day might hold. The Hearth still feels like a refuge, the memory of last night lingering warmly between you and Kira as you ready yourselves for the next steps in your journey.\n\nWhat would you like to do as you begin this new day in Marrow's Rest?",
  "actions": [
